Jun: Anything I can interest you in?
if State.garlic == "bought" && State.health_potion == "bought"
	- Back
		Jun: Thanks for your patronage!
		set State.player_can_move = true
		=> shopgreeting

elif State.health_potion == "bought"
	- Garlic
		set State.garlic = "bought"
		Jun: Excellent choice! => shop
	- Back
